00:18.500 --> 00:20.460
♪ Get those puppies! ♪

00:20.460 --> 00:22.380
♪ Can't catch
a furry flurry ♪

00:22.380 --> 00:24.120
♪ Running in a blurry hurry ♪

00:26.380 --> 00:27.540
♪ Get those puppies! ♪

00:28.920 --> 00:31.210
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:31.210 --> 00:32.750
♪ Canines on the run ♪

00:32.750 --> 00:34.620
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:34.620 --> 00:35.960
♪ Them doggone dogs are fun ♪

00:35.960 --> 00:37.460
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:37.460 --> 00:40.120
♪ Without fail you'll wind up
chasing your tail ♪

00:40.120 --> 00:42.120
♪ What's the harm
in ruffling some feathers ♪

00:42.120 --> 00:44.040
♪

00:44.040 --> 00:45.250
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:46.250 --> 00:47.580
♪ Life's just a bed of roses ♪

00:47.580 --> 00:49.040
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:49.040 --> 00:51.080
♪ Fast friends
with cold, wet noses ♪

00:51.080 --> 00:53.170
-♪ 1-0-1 ♪
-♪ Through thick, thin,
